Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:15.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}桃色そよ風が　わたしを包み込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:17.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}背中押してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}「さあ、行こう、ほら」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:23.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}大切なもの　探すのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:26.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}見たことないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:31.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}ステキに会える予感だけ持ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:34.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}それで十分でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:37.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}広がるファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}今を超えて　その旅路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}止まれない　すぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:47.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}Follow Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:50.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}愛・愛・愛を引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}素直なBRAVE　踏み出せば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:58.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}描ききれない  地図のカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:22:59.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}絶対！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}愛　会いたいと思うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:05.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}強気なBREATH　吸い込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:10.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}夢の続きにまた夢を見よう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:20.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}あなたと　叶えたい　明日へ
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:15.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}桃色微风将我包裹起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:17.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}推动我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}「来吧  出发  赶紧」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:23.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}寻找重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:26.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}就要向着未曾见过的那片地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:31.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}如果预感能与你完美邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:34.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}那样就足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:37.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}延伸的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}跨越现在  踏上那段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}已经  无法停止脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:47.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}Follow Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:50.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}爱·爱·爱  带上我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}率直的BRAVE  只要迈出这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:58.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}无法绘制完毕  地图的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:22:59.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}绝对！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}只要念着遇见爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:05.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}深吸一口积极的BREATH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:10.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}在梦的续篇继续邂逅美梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:20.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}想要和你  一起实现  向着明天
